<Box display="flex" flexDirection="column" gap="1.5rem">
  {friends.map((friend) => (
    <Friend
      key={`${friend._id}-${friend.firstName}-${friend.lastName}`}
      friendId={friend._id}
      name={`${friend.firstName} ${friend.lastName}`}
      subtitle={friend.occupation}
      userPicturePath={friend.picturePath}
    />
  ))}
</Box>;
